Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:10.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to be by your side more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:15.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:21.36,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I... to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:23.12,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...might love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.95,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Queen's {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Holiday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.95,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Queen's {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Holiday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Underground Secret Document
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes Chevalier de Milan at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you completed your research?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a prime example of how it's dark at the base of a lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you arrest and prosecute him immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The testimony of the Musketeer Force's former vice-captain is not enough to incriminate the Chair President of Legal Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us proceed with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But would that not endanger you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reliable bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only have you given rank and a title to a plebeian like myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you even gave me a chance to take revenge upon my foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here {\i1}again{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get along with that owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came because Agnes told us to stand by at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be an important mission from Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go. {this on'es having an out-of-keyframe experience}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all look wonderful, my dear fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It has been a while, Master Scarron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tres bien!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what brings you two here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's with your costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we're going to be in the Taniariji Royal Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beauty has finally been accepted by the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Vacances en Tristania"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a little short on staff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, my dear fairies, time to open the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.59,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Um{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you two spacing out over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop blabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you go to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you go change with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off you go, get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I look more natural in this than in my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.28,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number one is definitely Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number two's Marlene,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and number three's Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last place is definitely Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of ranking was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's breast{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mere dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act like a dog and bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise-chan, you got a nomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Julio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute in that outfit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told by Agnes to stand by at this shop, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how many times do we have to toast before you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun no matter how many times you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is a great shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he come all the way here just to meddle with Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is there a shop called "Charming Fairy Inn" around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.17,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search that side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have gone to the Kurdone alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened, but let me go get Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to borrow {\i1}your{\i0} strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my bodyguard for several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Queen, so shouldn't you have\Nbodyguards who are more suitable than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must act while undercover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was why you told us to be here on standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Since it's a request from none other than the Queen, I'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't anything dangerous, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to put you in danger, who knows what Louise would do to me later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's make our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The security guards will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stay here for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, could you lend me some clothes that would make me look like a plebeian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise's skirt is about the only thing we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can she even fit into Louise's clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shirt's a little small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show's tonight, so let's close the shop early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.23,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's closing already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's toast some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, she never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Identify yourselves and indicate your destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off your hood and show us your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they formed a security line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A search order has been issued to\Nthe soldiers for a missing aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in other words, they're looking for {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll suspect us even more if we were to hide our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, please put your arm around my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think we're really standing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep playing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search the other street!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Lishman-dono that Agnes of Her\NHighness' Musketeer Force has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's urgent news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent news, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be an absolute emergency for the captain to come all the way to the Chair President of Legal Affair's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just had a similar kidnapping case the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your unit made to display incompetence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are searching for her in order to not present ourselves as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would like your permission to block off major roads and ports.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search for Her Highness with everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't find her, by the name of Legal Affairs, I'll have you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm researching the case regarding the Protestants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you were involved in that case twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who proposed the Massacre of Dungletale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Massacre?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me the villain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in the village were planning to overturn the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a justified mission of suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppression. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for records of that instance, but I can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would know who the captain of that mission was, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than what happened twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't you be prioritising the search for Her Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Saito go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this room really acceptable for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, what horrible rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'll rain all night long at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you... hold my shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She feels like ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! We're from the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency! We'll force it open if we must!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many soldiers out in the street, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to explain right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:36.56,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me an explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master is waiting at the usual theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Queen has been kidnapped by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess... what are we doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to lure out the traitor, we issued a\Nfalse emergency stating that I went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they're unlikely to fall for misinformation so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I seriously ran as hard as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As hard as you could? But what if something were to happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked you to be my bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to protect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like you would Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was fooled by you as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a saying about deceiving the ally before you deceive the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time. Let us go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito's with Her Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We needed Saito to be Her Highness' bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Was I just an extra, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, until everything is done, be on standby at that shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? The show's going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tear-jerking play performed by the Scarron family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.31,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a move, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you with Her Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, until a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's with Agnes right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, what are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's show time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called the Liar's Mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a liar puts their hand inside, they won't be able to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try and put your hand inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! It's too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.33,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dog even in the play...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Her Highness has yet to be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows where she is right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lishman-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that you'd hurry and make\Ncontact with the spy if I went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you rush, the less careful you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a cautious rat will show its tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So your going missing was a trick to lure me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lishman, Chair President of Legal Affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are under arrest for treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curtain has dropped, Lishman-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still naive, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Henrietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be from Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest for spying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Lishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theatre is under my jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my ways around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going, Lishman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be caught by an ex-plebeian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of catching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dungletale...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My home vanished without being guilty of any crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you're a survivor from that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time I take my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kill you in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. The record from Dungletale you're\Nlooking for is kept underneath the Magic Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taste the fang we plebeians sharpened to use against you aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die from the bite of the fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what were you doing with Her Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell Her Highness' perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be her bodyguard unless you're so\Nclose to her that her perfume sticks onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do something to Her Highness by any chance, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of that, what were {\i1}you{\i0} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You dare doubt your master, dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better tell the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.27,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing with the maid in the school's basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sailor uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Underground Secret Document.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
